                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>New York</placeName>\n                <date>Aug<lb/> 8/62</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <sic>\n                    <addressee>Revd. Leaser</addressee>\n                </sic>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Dr Sir</p>\n            <p>Pardon the liberty I take<lb/> in addressing these lines to you<lb/> but it is\n                respecting that gentleman<lb/>\n                <persName>Mr. L. L. Levy</persName>, whom I called<lb/> on when in your city, as he\n                was<lb/> kind enough to offer to assist<lb/> me a little, hearing of my\n                misfortune.<lb/> Hearing <persName>Mr Levy</persName> has lost my<lb/> address which\n                I left with him<lb/> and do not know <sic>wich</sic> way to<lb/> write so I could\n                hear from<lb/> himâ€”sir as you are so well<lb/> acquainted with <persName>Mr\n                    Levy</persName><lb/> should I trouble you to call<lb/> on that Gentleman and\n                ask<lb/> of him kindly for me If he<lb/> can possibly render me some<lb/> aid. If\n                convenient I am<lb/> full aware it will be done</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p30c4t52f/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
