                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>for his feelings which he expressed<lb/> for me &amp; mine. Sir as I<lb/> still have\n                your No. in my<lb/> possession I have taken<lb/> the liberty of asking of<lb/> you\n                if you would call<lb/> on my friend for me.<lb/> And I hope Dr Sir you<lb/> will\n                return a reply to my<lb/> hasty scribble. If it is<lb/> not too much intrusion</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">Yours very Respect</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Mrs. E. S. Poznanski</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p>Residence</p>\n            <p>\n                <placeName>439</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>Hudson Street</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">\n                <placeName>N. Y.</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p>my respects</p>\n            <p>to <persName>Mr Levy</persName></p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
